timing_read_li...y_without_ecsm(25.10)  timing_read_li...y_without_ecsm(25.10)

Name
       timing_read_library_without_ecsm

Syntax
        timing_read_library_without_ecsm

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       Disables loading ECSM data.

       When  set  to true, the loading of ECSM data is disabled. If the timing
       library contains NLDM, ECSM, or CCS data in the same  file,  then  ECSM
       data will not be read.

       Note:  This global variable does not disable CCS data loading.

       To set this global variable, use the set_global command.

